OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Service records
OL,4,Chighest number of life-threatening
OL,5,Cemergencies
OL,7,FLondon Ambulance Service said it
OL,8,Frecorded the highest number of life-
OL,9,Fthreatening emergencies in its
OL,10,Fhistory, "driven by the extreme heat",
OL,11,Fon Wednesday.
OL,13,FAmbulance crews responded to a record
OL,14,F642 category one calls on Wednesday
OL,15,Famid a rare red warning for extreme
OL,16,Fheat.
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@eO]
