OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Service records
OL,4,Chighest number of life-threatening
OL,5,Cemergencies
OL,7,FCategory one incidents include the
OL,8,Fmost serious, life-threatening
OL,9,Finjuries and illnesses such as cardiac
OL,10,Farrests and patients who are not
OL,11,Fbreathing.
OL,13,FChief executive Jason Killens said:
OL,14,F"We have seen the highest number of
OL,15,Flife-threatening emergencies in our
OL,16,Fhistory, driven by the extreme heat
OL,17,Facross London.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
