OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782406081
OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Service records
OL,4,Chighest number of life-threatening
OL,5,Cemergencies
OL,7,F"Our crews are working very hard in
OL,8,Fchallenging conditions to care for
OL,9,Fpatients, and I would like to take
OL,10,Fthis opportunity to thank all our
OL,11,Fpeople for their incredible hard work.
OL,13,F"Please help them to help you by
OL,14,Ftaking care of yourself and others `
OL,15,Fstay out of the sun and keep hydrated."
OL,17,FIt was the fifth busiest day in the
OL,18,Fservice's history with 7,900 calls in
OL,19,Ftotal and ambulance crews responding
OL,20,Fto nearly 3,600 patients.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
