OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782406081
OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Service records
OL,4,Chighest number of life-threatening
OL,5,Cemergencies
OL,7,FThe rise in calls is linked to the hot
OL,8,Fweather, with crews responding to more
OL,9,Fpeople who are fainting, struggling to
OL,10,Fbreathe or experiencing heart
OL,11,Fproblems, the service said.
OL,13,FLondon Ambulance Service has put more
OL,14,Fthan 400 additional ambulance crews on
OL,15,Fthe road this week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
