OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782406081
OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Service records
OL,4,Chighest number of life-threatening
OL,5,Cemergencies
OL,7,FThe service has warned that patients
OL,8,Fcan become seriously unwell very
OL,9,Fquickly in the heat. Even after
OL,10,Ftemperatures begin to fall,
OL,11,Frespiratory and heart-related
OL,12,Fincidents can increase in the days
OL,13,Ffollowing a heatwave.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
