FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782406081
OL,3,CLondon Ambulance Service records
OL,4,Chighest number of life-threatening
OL,5,Cemergencies
OL,7,FAs well as extra ambulance crews,
OL,8,FLondon Ambulance Service has increased
OL,9,Fchecks on patients who are waiting for
OL,10,Fhelp. This allows clinicians in the
OL,11,F999 control room to identify if a
OL,12,Fpatient's condition is deteriorating
OL,13,Fand ensure the most seriously ill are
OL,14,Fprioritised, the service said.
